Power BI | Retail & Quick Commerce Analytics

ğŸš€ Project Overview

This project presents a Power BI dashboard built using BlinkIT grocery sales data, focused on converting raw transactional data into decision-ready business insights for retail and quick-commerce operations.

Instead of basic reporting, the dashboard emphasizes category performance, outlet contribution, sales efficiency, and demand patterns, enabling stakeholders to make data-driven decisions related to inventory, merchandising, and outlet strategy.

